tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE coordinates (coordinate_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
lat DECIMAL(9,6) NOT NULL,
long DECIMAL(9,6) NOT NULL,
region_id INT,
FOREIGN KEY (region_id) REFERENCES region(region_id));

CREATE TABLE population_stats (stat_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
region_id INT,
year INT,
population_size INT,
FOREIGN KEY (region_id) REFERENCES region(region_id));

CREATE TABLE heatmap_data (data_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
coordinate_id INT,
population_density INT,
FOREIGN KEY (coordinate_id) REFERENCES coordinates(coordinate_id));
